### Third-Party Components in This Repository

This repository contains no third-party code, geometry, or assets.  
All models are original Dmension engine outputs.

GLB files use the glTF 2.0 specification (Khronos Group, open standard) and the following ratified extensions:
- `KHR_lights_punctual` — Khronos Group, ratified extension
- `KHR_materials_emissive_strength` — Khronos Group, ratified extension

These extensions are part of the open glTF ecosystem and their use does not create any IP obligation.

